OL,3,CBirds to be culled over suspected
OL,4,Cavian flu outbreak in Omagh
OL,6,FA suspected case of bird flu has been
OL,7,Fflagged in Omagh, Co Tyrone prompting
OL,8,Fdisease control measures to be put in
OL,9,Fplace.
OL,11,F"Humane culling" of all birds on the
OL,12,Fsite of the potential outbreak and the
OL,13,Fintroduction of temporary control
OL,14,Fzones have been advised by the chief
OL,15,Fveterinary officer (CVO) for Northern
OL,16,FIreland Brian Dooher.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
