OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772718050
OL,3,CBirds to be culled over suspected
OL,4,Cavian flu outbreak in Omagh
OL,6,FThe Agriculture minister Andrew Muir
OL,7,Fsaid the potential case of notifiable
OL,8,Fhighly pathogenic avian influenza
OL,9,F(HPAI) was reported on Tuesday at a
OL,10,Fcommercial poultry premises.
OL,12,F"The CVO has, therefore, taken the
OL,13,Fdecision, as a precautionary measure,
OL,14,Fto apply appropriate disease control
OL,15,Fmeasures, including the humane culling
OL,16,Fof all poultry on the site and the
OL,17,Fintroduction of temporary control
OL,18,Fzones (TCZ) to mitigate for onward
OL,19,Fdisease spread," he said.
OL,26,@tD@AOU{D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
