CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772718050
OL,3,CBirds to be culled over suspected
OL,4,Cavian flu outbreak in Omagh
OL,6,FMr Dooher said the controlled zone and
OL,7,Fculling on the site were "crucial to
OL,8,Flimit any potential spread of disease".
OL,10,F"I appeal to all bird owners `
OL,11,Fbackyard and commercial ` to take all
OL,12,Fnecessary steps to protect your
OL,13,Fflock," he said.
OL,15,F"This includes ensuring continuous
OL,16,Fexcellent levels of biosecurity and
OL,17,Freporting any suspect cases of avian
OL,18,Fflu to Daera immediately.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUpD@fO]rD@AOUuD@GO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
