FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772718050
OL,3,CBirds to be culled over suspected
OL,4,Cavian flu outbreak in Omagh
OL,6,F"Samples from the infected premises
OL,7,Fhave been sent to the National
OL,8,FReference Laboratory to confirm strain
OL,9,Fand pathogenicity.
OL,11,F"Should HPAI be officially confirmed,
OL,12,Fthese TCZs will be revoked and
OL,13,Freplaced with a three kilometre
OL,14,Fprotection zone (PZ) and 10 kilometre
OL,15,Fsurveillance zone (SZ)."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@XO]
