OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1772718050
OL,3,CBirds to be culled over suspected
OL,4,Cavian flu outbreak in Omagh
OL,6,FThe avian influenza prevention zone
OL,7,F(AIPZ) for the whole of Northern
OL,8,FIreland remains in place, which means
OL,9,Fit is a legal requirement for all
OL,10,Fpoultry and other captive birds to be
OL,11,Fhoused or otherwise kept separate from
OL,12,Fwild birds.
OL,14,FAs part of the prevention zones, bird
OL,15,Fkeepers must follow strict biosecurity
OL,16,Fmeasures to mitigate against disease
OL,17,Fincursion.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/6
