OL,3,CBirds to be culled over suspected
OL,4,Cavian flu outbreak in Omagh
OL,6,FA ban on the gatherings of galliforme
OL,7,F(including pheasants, partridge,
OL,8,Fquail, chickens, turkey, guinea fowl),
OL,9,Fanseriforme (including ducks, geese,
OL,10,Fswans) and poultry is also in force.
OL,12,FThe Public Health Agency has confirmed
OL,13,Favian influenza is primarily a disease
OL,14,Fof birds and the risk to the general
OL,15,Fpublic's health is very low.
